the siliconbase workspace control center of the sage air defense system the first real time computerized military system the workspace workspace resources are divided into three categories the archives the classroom and the web workshop the archives browse search and retrieve text images video and audio from the siliconbase archive the classroom search a collection of student work browse through siliconbase digital course readers and access important information on the role of information technology in education the web workshop download the tools necessary for conducting research in siliconbase search the siliconbase record of other web sites committed to exploring the digital age copyright 1996 itsp all rights reserved questions comments bugs send mail to the itsp web master
